    <h3 id="in_this_tutorial"></h3>

    <p>This tutorial first introduces you to &brandShortName;'s User
    Interface. This is followed by a basic formatting section. Next
    secion, tells you how to insert elements like images, tables, and
    forms in your document. Then we have small section devoted to
